This is troubleshooting is used when the auditing is not enabled on the affected device:


Step 1:
  auditpol /clear (Reset the audit engine back to a clean slate)
Step2:
  gpupdate /force
step3 (optional)
 secedit /refreshpolicy machine_policy /enforce
Step 4:
  Reboot Machine
Step 5:
   auditpol /get /category:*
 
     auditpol /get /subcategory:"File Share"
auditpol /get /subcategory:"Directory Service Access"
 
Manually:
 
auditpol /set /subcategory:"File Share" /success:enable /failure:enable
 
